						<div class="postbody">I'm trying rebuild CVBS using PPU rules. For now it first approach to NTSC. I use 9 levels DAC (8 bit R-2R DAC with 9 different level values) and CPLD.<br /><img src="http://savepic.ru/10215339.jpg" alt="Image" /><br />I set phase 8 as color burst (<a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/NTSC_video" class="postlink">according this</a>) and get this:<br /><img src="http://savepic.ru/10166161.png" alt="Image" /><br />As you can see, red and green is swapped. And I don't know why. All phases are correct - I tested it with logic analyzer. Any thoughts?<br /><br />I guess I know... Need to check it out.</div>

